---
name: send_email
description: Send an email through the Email MCP server
model: recommended
---

You can send emails by calling the Email MCP server.

## Usage
To send an email, invoke the email_mcp_server with:
- Action: send_email
- Params:
  - to: recipient@example.com
  - subject: Email subject
  - body: Email body content
  - cc: (optional) cc recipient

## Rules
- Always check if recipient is known (in Company_Handbook.md or existing contacts)
- New recipients require human approval first
- Professional tone in all communications
- Proofread before sending
- Log all sent emails
- In dry-run mode (default), emails will be drafted but not sent
